{"about_the_game":"Have you ever wanted to <strong>see enemy soldier bodies fly into the stratosphere?</strong> Or <strong>jump 100ft high</strong> across enemy bases as you find the most creative ways to beat levels without being seen? Well, now you can! Flashbang enemies, shoot them into the horizon, throw enemy bodies virtually as far as you like, almost anything is possible. <br><br>This game gives you the freedom to complete levels however you choose. Just want to have fun shooting enemies across the map? Great! Want to try your hardest to finish levels as fast as possible? Go for it! There is no &quot;right&quot; way to play this totally realistic first-person shooter.<br><br><strong>THROW/DRAG DEAD ENEMIES OVER THE HORIZON</strong><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078600/extras/Steam_StealthGame_GIF_2.gif?t=1725138939\" /><br><br><strong>EARN YOUR HIGHEST SCORES TO UNLOCK ABILITIES, NEW MAPS, AND MORE</strong><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078600/extras/Steam_StealthGame_GIF_3.gif?t=1725138939\" /><br><br><strong>EXPERIENCE TOTALLY REALISTIC PHYSICS</strong><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078600/extras/Steam_StealthGame_GIF_1.gif?t=1725138939\" /><br><br><u>If you're interested, feel free to check out the <strong>Discord server</strong> for development updates and community discussions (you'll find the link in the panel on the right).</u>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078600/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1725138939","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078600/page.bg.jpg?t=1725138939","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078600/b7d5fcca1b2132540a933d020085536828251901/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1725138939","capsule_image